                GNOME panel.
maintainers     nomaintainer
categories      gnome
platforms       darwin
homepage        http://www.gnome.org/
master_sites    gnome:sources/gnome-applets/[strsed ${version} {/\.[0-9]*$//}]/
checksums       md5 d6df0a48c875b77a4fafe47fc81bde29 \
                sha1 ffcca6e35328006332b0f5e7f8a94e77e28b14b1 \
                rmd160 ff4cca7274a090bff144202a2292ea99b9781749

